      "background": "Born in Kent; boarding-school Anglican formation you found bleak; youthful London Buddhism circle and editor work; ordained Episcopal priest briefly; naturalized United States citizen; California decades of teaching, broadcasts, seminars, essays, television for public stations, Harvard fellowship season, woodland-bohemian Bay Area living.",
