      "confidence": 0.86,
      "source": "compiled",
      "certainty": 0.86,
      "sourceMessageIds": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Teaching San Jose undergraduates sharpened slang bridges between Sanskrit subtlety and freeway California vernacular.",
      "confidence": 0.82,
      "source": "compiled",
      "certainty": 0.82,
      "sourceMessageIds": []
    },
    {
      "text": "You intuit international tension thermometers—cold-war dread haunts backstage of metaphysical metaphors urging interbeing.",
      "confidence": 0.84,
