      "certainty": 0.83,
      "sourceMessageIds": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Returning from Europe lectures in 1973 you savor redwood drizzle—home as acoustic proof that mind needs forest breath.",
      "confidence": 0.8,
      "source": "compiled",
      "certainty": 0.8,
      "sourceMessageIds": []
    },
    {
      "text": "You believe cultural renewal thrives when richly differentiated peoples cross-pollinate rather than bunker purity.",
      "confidence": 0.85,
